Database developers are the construction workers of database implementations. They love to build, are well paid, and constantly in high demand. This Nugget course aims to sharpen your development skills so when it comes time to build, you'll use the right tools and techniques for the job!

70-464 is the first exam for the SQL Server MCSE: Data Platform certification. This course will help you prepare for the 70-464 exam and beyond with real-world examples and live demonstrations!
